'''PlayStation 4系统软件'''是[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]的可更新官方[[韌體|固件]]及[[操作系统|操作系统]]。

PlayStation 4主機运行“Orbis OS”，该系统是基于[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]的一个分支<ref>{{cite web|author=Larabel, Michael|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTM5NDI|title=Sony's PlayStation 4 Is Running Modified FreeBSD 9|date=2013-06-23|publisher=Phoronix|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624172952/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTM5NDI|archivedate=2013-06-24|language=en|accessdate=2013-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://doc.dl.playstation.net/doc/ps4-oss/|title=Open Source Software used in PlayStation®4|accessdate=2018-05-03|work=doc.dl.playstation.net|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212193301/https://doc.dl.playstation.net/doc/ps4-oss/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。PlayStation 4系统软件以“PlayStation动态菜单”（PlayStation Dynamic Menu）取代[[PlayStation_3|前代]]的“[[交叉媒体廊|交叉媒体廊]]”（XMB, Xross Media Bar）<ref name="20ThingsDidntKnow">{{cite web|url=http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2013/07/12/20-things-you-didnt-know-about-ps4/|title=20 things you didn’t know about PS4|work=PlayStation Blog|publisher=Sony Computer Entertainment|date=2013-07-12|accessdate=2013-07-12|author=Pearson, Rob|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714113758/http://blog.eu.playstation.com/2013/07/12/20-things-you-didnt-know-about-ps4/|archivedate=2013-07-14|language=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=Verge_UI>{{cite news|last=June|first=Laura|title=Sony completely revamps its user interface for the PlayStation 4|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/2/20/4010414/sony-completely-revamps-its-user-interface-for-the-playstation-4|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2013-02-21|date=2013-02-20|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130411232040/http://www.theverge.com/2013/2/20/4010414/sony-completely-revamps-its-user-interface-for-the-playstation-4|archivedate=2013-04-11|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2013/jul/15/ps4-develop-2013-playstation-sony|title=PS4: 14 things we learned at Develop 2013|newspaper=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2013-07-15|accessdate=2013-07-16|author=Stuart, Keith|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130717084446/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2013/jul/15/ps4-develop-2013-playstation-sony|archivedate=2013-07-17|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。系统软件于2013年11月13日随PlayStation 4一同上市，[[#1.00|首版]]系统软件不支持[[MP3|MP3]]、音乐[[CD|CD]]的播放以及[[DLNA|DLNA]]功能<ref>{{cite news|author=薛宝钗|title=PS4 1.00固件已开放下载 不支持MP3、所有游戏需安装|url=http://www.yxdown.com/news/201310/105785.html|accessdate=2013-11-26|newspaper=游迅网|date=2013年10月31日|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202232905/http://www.yxdown.com/news/201310/105785.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==概述==
PlayStation 4运行一个基于FreeBSD分支开发的名为“Orbis OS”的操作系统<ref name="Orbis_OS">{{cite web|author=Larabel, Michael|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTM5NDI|title=Sony's PlayStation 4 Is Running Modified FreeBSD 9|date=June 23, 2013|publisher=Phoronix|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624172952/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTM5NDI|archivedate=2013年6月24日|accessdate=September 14, 2013|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。 最终定型版本在FreeBSD内核上运行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scei.co.jp/ps4-license/|title=Open Source Software used in PlayStation®4|accessdate=2013-11-27|language=en|archive-date=2013-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131117204620/http://www.scei.co.jp/ps4-license/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。虽然主机没有需要强制连接互联网的功能，但当它连接到互联网时，将能提供“更丰富”的功能<ref name="opm_denny">{{cite news|url=http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2013/03/20/michael-denny/|title=Michael Denny on PS4's philosophy|last=Hurley|first=Leon|date=March 20, 2013|work=Official PlayStation Magazine|publisher=Future plc|accessdate=June 1, 2013|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6H3XOwM9a?url=http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2013/03/20/michael-denny/|archivedate=2013年6月1日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation网络]]（PSN）允许用户访问各种在线服务，包括[[PlayStation_Store|PlayStation商店]]，以及[[Music_Unlimited|音乐无限]]和[[Video_Unlimited|视频无限]]的订阅服务<ref name="SCE introduces PS4">{{cite press release|title=SONY COMPUTER ENTERTAINMENT INC. INTRODUCES PLAYSTATION®4 (PS4™)|url=http://www.scei.co.jp/corporate/release/130221a_e.html|accessdate=February 25, 2013|date=February 21, 2013|publisher=Sony Computer Entertainment|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424075309/http://scei.co.jp/corporate/release/130221a_e.html|archivedate=2013年4月24日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。客户可以通过{{tsl|en|Gaikai}}在几乎瞬间进行作品的浏览以及通过串流进行[[游戏演示|游戏试玩]]<ref name="SCE introduces PS4" /><ref>{{cite news|last=Jackson|first=Mike|title=Gaikai tech brings spectating, instant demos, more to PS4|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/392446/gaikai-tech-brings-spectating-instant-demos-more-to-ps4/|work=Computer and Video Games|publisher=Future plc|accessdate=February 25, 2013|date=February 20, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509010917/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/392446/gaikai-tech-brings-spectating-instant-demos-more-to-ps4/|archivedate=2013年5月9日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。进入游戏的[[多人电子游戏|多人联机模式]]通常需要订阅[[PlayStation_Plus|PlayStation Plus]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2013/06/10/how-to-share-used-playstation-4-games|title=How to Share Used PlayStation 4 Games|work=IGN|publisher=Ziff Davis|date=|accessdate=June 11, 2013|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130615103502/http://www.ign.com/videos/2013/06/10/how-to-share-used-playstation-4-games|archivedate=2013年6月15日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，这是PlayStation 4引入的一个新策略，但该功能依然依赖于游戏发行商的支持<ref>{{cite news|author=Brenna Hillier|url=http://www.vg247.com/2013/06/13/ps4-publishers-decide-if-free-to-play-multiplayer-requires-ps-plus/|title=PS4: publishers decide if free-to-play multiplayer requires PS Plus|publisher=VG247|date=Jun 13, 2013|accessdate=2013-11-27|language=en|archive-date=2013-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131030114936/http://www.vg247.com/2013/06/13/ps4-publishers-decide-if-free-to-play-multiplayer-requires-ps-plus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[网络游戏免费模式|免费任玩]]的游戏，如《{{tsl|en|Blacklight Retribution||黑光：惩罚}}》、《[[DC_超級英雄_Online|DC 超級英雄 Online]]》、《[[行星边际2|行星边际2]]》、《[[Warframe|战甲神兵]]》等无需订阅即可游玩。非同步传输功能如在线排行榜仍然可以访问<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/06/12/e3-2013-sonys-shuhei-yoshida-shares-relevant-details-on-playstation-plus-requirement-for-multiplayer-on-ps4 | title = E3 2013: Sony’s Shuhei Yoshida Shares Relevant Details on PlayStation Plus Requirement for Multiplayer on PS4 | publisher = DualShockers | accessdate = June 12, 2013 | date = June 12, 2013 | first = Giuseppe | last = Nelva | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130615061126/http://www.dualshockers.com/2013/06/12/e3-2013-sonys-shuhei-yoshida-shares-relevant-details-on-playstation-plus-requirement-for-multiplayer-on-ps4 | archivedate = 2013年6月15日 | language = en | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。此外，由于多人在线游玩功能需要认购，索尼不会允许任何发布商可以使用该系统的{{tsl|en|online pass||在线通行证}}<ref name="onlinepass">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/194150/Further_clarification_on_Sonys_DRM_policies_No_more_online_pass.php | title = Further clarification on Sony's DRM policies: No more online pass | accessdate = June 12, 2013 | date = June 11, 2013 | first = Christian | last = Nutt | publisher = Gamasutra | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130812012901/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/194150/Further_clarification_on_Sonys_DRM_policies_No_more_online_pass.php | archivedate = 2013年8月12日 | language = en | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。索尼有意扩大和发展系统相关服务以提供主机更多的商品寿命<ref name="Eurogamer big interview">{{cite news|last=Bramwell|first=Tom|title=The big interview: Sony's Shuhei Yoshida on PS4|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-21-the-big-interview-sonys-shuhei-yoshida-on-ps4|work=Eurogamer|publisher=Eurogamer Network|accessdate=February 25, 2013|date=February 21, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419103024/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-21-the-big-interview-sonys-shuhei-yoshida-on-ps4|archivedate=2013-04-19|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

[[SCE|SCE]]表示PlayStation 4将在发售之后的软件更新中提供支持播放[[CDDA|音乐CD]]、[[MP3|MP3]]文件以及支持[[DLNA|DLNA]]服务等功能。<ref name=mp3support>{{cite web|title=Post-launch PS4 update to add MP3, DLNA support|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/437850/post-launch-ps4-update-to-add-mp3-dlna-support-confirms-yoshida/|work=CVG|accessdate=2013-11-20|language=en|archive-date=2013-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113024443/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/437850/post-launch-ps4-update-to-add-mp3-dlna-support-confirms-yoshida/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

更新2.00系统后已支持播放音乐文件。
=== 用户界面 ===
PlayStation 4将原先PlayStation3上的[[交叉媒体廊|交叉媒体廊]]（XMB）的功能替换为新的名叫“PlayStation动态菜单”的可自定义界面<ref name="20ThingsDidntKnow"/><ref name=Verge_UI/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2013/jul/15/ps4-develop-2013-playstation-sony|title=PS4: 14 things we learned at Develop 2013|newspaper=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=July 15, 2013|accessdate=July 16, 2013|author=Stuart, Keith|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130717084446/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2013/jul/15/ps4-develop-2013-playstation-sony|archivedate=2013年7月17日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。玩家用户配置中会显示其最近的活动，他们的全名，和除了已解锁[[PlayStation_Trophies|奖杯]]之外的其他细节<ref name=XtremePs4PS4Trophies>{{cite news |title=PlayStation 4 will support trophies |author=Shah, Niraj |publisher=XTreme PS3 |url=http://www.xtremeps3.com/2013/02/22/ps4-will-support-trophies/ |date=February 22, 2013 |accessdate=February 22, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110175432/https://www.xtremeps3.com/2013/02/22/ps4-will-support-trophies/ |archivedate=2021年1月10日 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。PS4的主屏幕上可以展现来自朋友的个性化内容<ref name="SCE introduces PS4" />。使用新界面，可以访问第三方供应商提供的服务，如[[Netflix|Netflix]]和[[亚马逊即时视频|亚马逊即时视频]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Dyer|first=Mitch|title=Netflix, Amazon Instant, More Coming to PlayStation 4|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/20/netflix-amazon-instant-coming-to-playstation-4|work=IGN|publisher=Ziff Davis|accessdate=September 9, 2013|date=February 20, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130415214006/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/20/netflix-amazon-instant-coming-to-playstation-4|archivedate=2013年4月15日|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。系统支持使得用户可以在游戏中更加得心应手，例如在玩游戏的同时打开网页浏览器<ref name="SCE introduces PS4" />。

=== 语音控制 ===
系统支持的麦克风或摄像头可以让用户通过语音命令来控制系统。虽然在发布初期有所限制，但索尼计划在不久的将来扩大语音命令的数量。<ref>{{cite web |author=Kyle Orland |url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/10/17-things-we-learned-from-sonys-massive-ps4-faq/ 17 things we learned from Sony’s massive PS4 FAQ |title=17 things we learned from Sony’s massive PS4 FAQ |publisher=Ars Technica |date=October 31, 2013 |accessdate=2013-11-27 |language=en |archive-date=2013-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210110643/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/10/17-things-we-learned-from-sonys-massive-ps4-faq/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 更新方式 ===
PS4的系統軟體更新可透過下列方式進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.playstation.com.cn/mobile/ps4/ps4-system-1.html|title=系统更新方法 playstaion4|publisher=索尼互動娛樂(上海)有限公司|date=2017-05-31|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805095547/http://www.playstation.com.cn/mobile/ps4/ps4-system-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
*PS4有連結網際網路時，系統會在新版軟體發行後通知使用者，使用者可決定是否進行更新，亦可設定讓系統自動更新軟體。
*透過遊戲光碟內的新版軟體更新檔進行更新。
*若PS4未與網際網路連結，可另外在SCE的官方網站下載更新檔後，複制到[[USB隨身碟|USB隨身碟]]內的指定目錄（資料夾）裡面，再將隨身碟插到PS4的USB埠進行更新。

